ttps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kali-Uchis.-CREDIT_-Omar-Vega_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kali-Uchis.-CREDIT_-Omar-Vega_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kali-Uchis.-CREDIT_-Omar-Vega_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Kali-Uchis.-CREDIT_-Omar-Vega_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kali-uchis">卡利·乌奇斯（Kali Uchis）</a>对她即将发行的新专辑进行了更新，称其重点是“改变生活的活动”。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kali-uchis-orquideas-review-lyrics-tracklist-3569143">Kali Uchis  - &#39;Orquídeas&#39;评论：无所畏惧的拉丁流行大使</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位美国 - 哥伦比亚歌手于2024年1月分享了“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kali-uchis-orquideas-review-lyrics-tracklist-3569143">Orquídeas</a> ”，然后在8月份<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kali-uchis-announces-new-lp-orquideas-parte-2-shares-kaytranada-remix-snippet-3780624">的OrquídeasParte 2&#39;</a> 。<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/best-albums-of-2024-so-far-3767987">迄今为止，前者登陆了<em>NME</em>的2024年最佳专辑</a>。</p><p>现在，在对<a href="https://10magazine.com/kali-uchis-on-motherhood-and-imminent-new-music/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>10本杂志</em></a>的新采访中，她透露自己正在研究下一张唱片，这源于“改变生活的活动”。</p><p> “Actually, in a very mystical and beautiful way, I&#39;ve had the honour of my albums becoming more meaningful than I even planned them to be because of the course that my life has taken,” she told the magazine.</p><p> Though she didn&#39;t mention what the event in question was, she shared that the entire record is dedicated to it, including the yet-to-be-revealed release date.</p><p> “这张专辑是关于生活的复杂性，尽管世界有世界，但仍在寻找生活中的喜悦。寻找欣赏每一刻的方法，而不是将生命视为理所当然。每天特别享受特别的。”她说。 “这是我最存在和诚实的工作。对我来说，这绝对是最美丽的工作，对我来说，这将是最有意义和最有影响力的。”</p><p> Uchis went on to say that the album will be entirely in English, saying that it became “a lot more meaningful” following “the turn of events that happened in my life.” </p><figure id="attachment_3406082" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3406082" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3406082" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/KaliUchis_2023_3.jpg" alt="卡利·乌奇斯（Kali Uchis）" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/KaliUchis_2023_3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/KaliUchis_2023_3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/KaliUchis_2023_3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/KaliUchis_2023_3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/KaliUchis_2023_3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/02/KaliUchis_2023_3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3406082" class="wp-caption-text">卡利·乌奇斯（Kali Uchis）。图片来源：Stephane Cardinale  -  Corbis/Corbis通过Getty Images</figcaption></figure><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/kali-uchis-orquideas-review-lyrics-tracklist-3569143"><em>NME</em> reviewed &#39;Orquídeas&#39; upon its release, giving it four stars</a> : “Uchis masterfully melds her bicultural worlds in the dembow-driven &#39;Muñekita&#39;.她与城市女孩的JT和多米尼加说唱歌手El Alfa一起穿着凶猛而怪异的曲目，讲述了一个女人在俱乐部中过着最好的生活。 Uchis后来在“ TuCorazónEsMío”的Spanglish中敞开心heart，其中用Don Toliver泄露了她的怀孕。</p><p> “Backed by lush R&amp;B production with Latin percussion, she showers her baby on the way with loving lyrics: <i>“I know that you&#39;re mine entirely / All that you need&#39;s inside of me,”</i> Uchis sings in Spanish.</p><p> “Through her boundless &#39;Orquídeas&#39; albums, Uchis blossoms into a fearless pop ambassador at the forefront of breaking down the divide between music in English and Spanish.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kali-uchis-says-upcoming-new-album-is-about-a-life-altering-event-3846651">卡利·乌奇斯（Kali Uchis）帖子说，即将发行的新专辑是关于“改变生活的盛会”，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
