oads/2025/03/Frank-Beard-of-ZZ-Top.-CREDIT_-R.-Diamond_Getty-Images.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frank-Beard-of-ZZ-Top.-CREDIT_-R.-Diamond_Getty-Images-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frank-Beard-of-ZZ-Top.-CREDIT_-R.-Diamond_Getty-Images-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frank-Beard-of-ZZ-Top.-CREDIT_-R.-Diamond_Getty-Images-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frank-Beard-of-ZZ-Top.-CREDIT_-R.-Diamond_Getty-Images-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/Frank-Beard-of-ZZ-Top.-CREDIT_-R.-Diamond_Getty-Images-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/zz-top">ZZ Top</a>分享说，他们的鼓手弗兰克·比尔德（Frank Beard）将抽出时间进行“健康程序”。</p><p>乐队昨天（3月14日）发表声明，说胡须将“暂时”在持续的演出期间逐渐消失，该演出于3月5日开始，“要参加一个健康问题，需要在短期内将重点放在。”</p><p>胡须将由“德克萨斯同胞和长期技术成员，打击乐手和鼓手”约翰·道格拉斯（John Douglas）取代，他们说与该团体有着“密切的关系”，此前Beard于2002年在巴黎进行紧急阑尾切除术。</p><p>声明总结说：“他期待着快速康复。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DHOrG_JzBwE/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style